title: #13 Dr. Boniface Talks Marijuana + FunDip Gets High On Painkillers!
description: This week, Dr. Phyllis Bonafice stopped by to discuss the ins and outs of Marijuana usage and it's legalization. We also go through the #LAPDShooting point by point, Hillary's recent email scandal and listen to FunDip as he progressively gets more and more loopy on his newest pain-meds.
